---
title: Beef Burger & Creamy Pesto Dressing with Parmesan Fries & Mixed Salad
description: Tomato sauce is always classic on a burger, but this time we’ve swapped it out for one of our other favourite classics; creamy
pesto dressing. Served with Parmesan-coated fries, you’ll be thanking us all night for this easy and mouth-watering meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/nz-beef-burger-creamy-pesto-dressing-2604d516.jpg
